Package: pc047oma
Type: Package
Title: PC047 vCagAepitope Gut Microbiome Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Yuhang", "Gong",
      email = "gongyuhang2023@gmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre"),
      comment = c(ORCID = "")
    )
  )
Description: Gut microbiome analysis for PC047 vCagAepitope project.
    This project investigates how Helicobacter pylori CagA protein
    reshapes the gut microbiome in Apc-mutant mouse models of
    tumorigenesis. Analysis follows the OMA (Orchestrating Microbiome
    Analysis) framework and bioBakery 3 protocols, including alpha/beta
    diversity analysis, differential abundance testing, and functional
    profiling using Kraken2, Bracken, and HUMAnN4.
